headline: Property & Casualty Claims Division Manager at State Farm| CEO of EmpowHer | Host of The Hello MaximizHer Podcast ®| NAAWLI Brand Ambassador
summary:
Currently a Division Manager of Claims responsible for the facilitation of world class remarkable customer experiences.

Kara Barker is an accomplished senior leader with nearly 20 years of leadership experience at a Fortune 50 company, ranked 31 on Fortune 500.
 
A purpose-driven leader with a proven and recognized track record of delivering results, she has demonstrated an ability to accelerate change, solve problems, transform mindsets and teams, and collaborate with key stakeholders in support of business goals and strategic initiatives.

Kara is an insightful strategist, highly effective global influencer and thought provoker whose work complements her purpose and passion, which is to be of service to others, with a focus on women, and other marginalized communities.

Kara has been a catalyst for change and transformation across various disciplines and organizations. She exudes calm confidence when faced with tough leadership challenges on transition, personnel, production, and quality issues.

Kara is a dynamic speaker who has captivated audiences around the world with her charisma, energy and powerful gift of storytelling.

Known for her impact and leadership, Kara has captivated audiences around the world for over 10 years with her engaging style and has consistently been praised for her ability to provoke thought, inspire commitment while leaving audiences feeling empowered and motivated.

When she’s not leading in the corporate arena, she’s pouring her words into devotional books, writing reading plans for YouVersion and hosting her podcast The Hello Maximizer on Apple, Google Play, and Spotify. She’s written two globally recognized Christian devotional journals Hallelujahs and Hiccups and Breakthroughs and Bless You’s.

Outside of work, Kara spends her time giving back to the local and global communities through various educational and philanthropic initiatives and serve as a Board Member and Brand Ambassador for The National African American Women’s Leadership Institute 

While this is only a snapshot, I welcome the opportunity to discuss how I can make an immediate impact in your organization. 

To contact me or request my full resume, please send an email to karabarker1123@gmail.com.
